# services/
# - Business logic layer
# - Called by controllers, calls Repository for DB access
# - Handles things like: hashing passwords, generating JWT, checking stock
# Example files:
#   authService.js    → registerUser, loginUser, getMe
#   bookService.js    → getAllBooks, getBook, createBook, updateBook, deleteBook
#   orderService.js   → placeOrder, getUserOrders
#   emailService.js   → sendWelcomeEmail, sendOrderConfirmation
